				</div>
			</div>

			<div
				class="flex flex-col gap-y-5 w-full px-4 items-center justify-center h-[20%] md:hidden"
			>
				<a
					class="w-full border-[1px] border-blue-700 text-blue-700 text-opacity-80 rounded-3xl p-2 text-center"
					href="">Crear cuenta nueva</a
				>
				<img
					src="https://z-m-static.xx.fbcdn.net/rsrc.php/v3/yM/r/DDgwTv3JehF.png"
					alt="facebook"
					class="opacity-65 w-[60px]"
				/>
				<ul class="flex gap-x-2 text-[10px] opacity-70">
					<a href="">Informacion</a>
					<a href="">Ayuda</a>
					<a href="">Más</a>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
	<footer class="bg-white w-full px-8 py-4 hidden md:block xl:px-[150px] xl:pt-[30px]">
		<div class="">
			<ul
